snippet.title: Demeo Battles | Announcement Trailer | Meta Quest 2 + 3 + Pro
snippet.description:
Wishlist Demeo Battles now: https://metaque.st/45AxqeF

Let the battle commence! Demeo Battles is a competitive turn-based strategy game for 2-4 players. Choose your champion, assemble an army of monstrous minions, and team up with another champion in your quest for turn-based glory!

Follow us:
Website: https://resolutiongames.com/demeobattles 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DemeoBattles 
Discord: https://discord.gg/demeo
